	<h4>Coffee Works Mobile App</h4>
	<p>
		As a coffee roasting company, Coffee Works has served delicious coffee to local Sacramentans since 1982. Although their commitment to quality coffee hasn't changed, they wanted to interface with customers in a more modern way.
		Coffee Works already had a website utalizing WordPress, WooCommerce, and Paypal, which are all integrated into the mobile app. From the client's WordPress dashboard they can add products with a click of a button and it will show up on the website and in the app.
		When a customer purchases coffee the app will verify that the payment was approved by Paypal and the order will be sent to the WooCommerce dashboard for processing. This app was built with Ionic, Cordova, Angular, Jquery, HTML, and CSS.
